<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.5">
<l>maiyār taṭaṅkaṇ karuṅkūnta lāycci maṟaiya vaittatayir</l>
<l>neyyār pālō ṭamutuceyta nēmi yaṅkai māyaṉiṭam</l>
<l>ceyyā rāra liraikarutic ceṅkāl nārai ceṉṟaṇaiyum</l>
<l>poyyā nāviṉ maṟaiyāḷar puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of Māyaṉ with a discus in his lovely hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">who ate ghee and curds with much milk,</l>
<l>Which the herdess, with black hair and wide, kohl-adorned eyes, kept hidden,</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtankuṭi with Vedic experts whose tongues never lie,</l>
<l>Where red-legged herons draw near,</l>
<l rend="indent">coming [there] intent on the āral [fish] as prey which fill the paddy fields.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
